  "title": "Project Engineer",
  "description": "<p>.</p><p>Job Title:  Project Engineer<br /></p><p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><p>· Assist and support Project Manager in handling and monitoring the progress of project.</p><p>· Able to lead a team of workers</p><p>· Ensure smooth progress of site works.</p><p>· Assessing and managing safety hazards.</p><p>· Completing records for site reports.</p><p>· Attending site management meetings.</p><p>· Control and maintain the safe and smooth progress of works</p><p>· To co-ordinate with clients, main-con and workers on all project aspects to ensure smooth and timely implementation.</p><p>· Monitoring of site activities, material requisition, cost control, project supervision and schedule of works.</p><p>· Any other ad-hoc duties that may be assigned from time to time</p><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><p>· Degree in Civil Engineering or equivalent. Diploma holders or equivalent or mature candidate with relevant experience and proven track records will also be considered.</p><p>· Positive working attitude and ability to work in a fast-paced environment</p><p>Employment Type: Full Time</p><p>Flexible Work Arrangement</p><p></p>",
